<tr>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">&#xa0;</td>
<td class="org-left">cost</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>



<div id="outline-container-orgb27c5e6" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgb27c5e6">Escalado</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-orgb27c5e6">
<p>
Cambia el tamaño del objeto.
</p>

<table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides">


<colgroup>
<col  class="org-right" />

<col  class="org-right" />

